{"type": "article", "id": 18306, "title": "镶嵌办公桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-01T07:20:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 53, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606160101A0QrVYsvflTj3pKo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一张为开放空间设计的办公桌，所有组件都由 15 毫米厚的中密度纤维板制成，可以直接拼接而无需螺丝安装。桌子的中间可以镶嵌隔板，成为两边使用的办公桌。桌子的侧边有 120 度的角，三张桌子可以完整拼接在一起构成社区式的办公空间，很方便，也不会显得拥挤。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160059vZzBQLFJVIWxeclH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160100dugVskJiWc2GTabN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160100C5wSlnvqVFrj7QIx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160101dbSFU3eR79WkBJGI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49755501\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}